  "title": "💼📊 Sales & Marketing (Business Development)",
  "description": "<p>📍 Singapore | Full-Time | Career Growth</p><p>Join us and gain exposure to the <strong>business side of sales and marketing</strong> — from campaign execution to team leadership and client relations.</p><p>You’ll learn how to identify opportunities, build customer relationships, and contribute to business expansion through ethical, performance-driven strategies.</p><p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Individuals interested in entrepreneurship, leadership, and business growth<br /><br /><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><p><ul><li>💡 Interest in business and leadership</li><li>🎯 Results-driven and proactive</li><li>🤝 Strong interpersonal skills</li></ul></p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><p><ul><li>📈 Support business growth and campaigns</li><li>🤝 Build and maintain client relationships</li><li>👥 Learn team leadership and strategy execution</li></ul></p><p><strong>What You’ll Gain</strong></p><p><ul><li>💼 Business and entrepreneurial exposure</li><li>🚀 Leadership development pathway</li><li>💰 Uncapped incentives</li><li>✈️ Travelling Opportunities</li></ul></p>",
